0xD4EC7858.name: GET_HELI_GAS_TANK_HEALTH
0xD4EC7858.description: **Note** This native will always return `1000.0` unless [SET_VEHICLE_BODY_HEALTH](#\_0xB77D05AC8C78AADB), [SET_VEHICLE_ENGINE_HEALTH](#\_0x45F6D8EEF34ABEF1), or [SET_VEHICLE_PETROL_TANK_HEALTH](#\_0x70DB57649FA8D0D8) have been called with a value greater than `1000.0`.
0xD4EC7858.resultsDescription: Returns the current health of the helicopter's gas tank.
